                    <h3>THE CLINICAL EXCHANGE: Expert Perspectives on Treating and Managing Patients at High Risk for Fracture</h3>
                    <p></p><h3>
                        ABOUT:
                    </h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The Clinical Exchange: Expert Perspectives on Treating and Managing Patients at High Risk for Fracture is an interactive and evidence-based program developed by leading Canadian experts to address the importance of risk assessment, screening and management for all patients at high risk for fracture. This program aims to translate scientific and clinical evidence into practical steps and incorporates expert recommendations into practical strategies applicable to primary care practice.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p></p><h3>
                        FORMAT:
                    </h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>This program consists of a core didactic deck and 5 case-based modules.&nbsp; Each module includes interactive case-based discussion. &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
                        <li>Please decide on the modules which will be presented prior to submitting the New Event Request Form</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h3> CERTIFICATION:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>This Group Learning activity has been certified for up to 6 MAINPRO+ one-credit-per-hour credits by the CFPC. &nbsp;</li>
                        <li>The core deck and each case-based module has been developed to fit into a 60 minute presentation. Please reference the Process Manual for a detailed description of the program modules and the applicable credit hours.</li>
                        <li><strong>As per the CFPC guidelines for certified programs, speakers are required to use the presentation slides provided by the physician organization and are not permitted to make any changes to the program materials/slides.</strong>              </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p></p><h3>
                    PROGRAM MODULES:<br>
                    THE CLINICAL EXCHANGE: Expert Perspectives on Treating and Managing Patients
                    at High Risk for Fracture – Core Deck
                   
                    </h3>
                 
                        <ul>
                            <li>1 Mainpro+ Credit (60 minutes)</li>
